Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:40.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:44.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不…不喜歡自己的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.53,0:03:48.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,很喜歡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.41,0:03:51.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,大家也都說是個好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:53.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那…這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姓名解讀哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:01.34,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\frz359.5\move(852.8,-165.8,828.4,776,0,7320)}易懂的姓名解讀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:00.01,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz269.6\c&H824AC0&\move(784.8,287.2,784.8,1056.4,21,5986)}完全版
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:01.34,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz283.4\c&H6F7264&\fscx88\fscy61\move(830,-50,820.4,879,0,7320)}中目黑之母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:04:00.42,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\fs35\frz359.7\move(1176,250,1188,1059)}工作運\N財運\N戀愛運\N整體運\N\h\h\h\h等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,名字的占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在班上很流行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,筆畫數不是太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:08.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼  給爸爸也來測一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:10.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,已經測過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.10,0:04:12.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,整體運五星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,財運五星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,愛情運五星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作運五星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒有比這更好的筆畫了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:25.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:29.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只是  說是不宜從事藝術相關的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H8548D2&\3c&H3C5D9F&\pos(1358.4,22.4)}不宜從事的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1870.4,262.4)}藝術家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1745.6,260.8)\c&H653DD4&}漫畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1625.6,262.4)}畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1504,265.6)}書法家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1396.8,262.4)}小說家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1280,265.6)}作曲家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1873.6,576)}插畫師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1748.8,582.4)}YouTuber
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1640,584)}V家P主
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.62,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1520,571.2)}超媒體創作者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:33.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  爸爸是上班族所以沒問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:40.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸有個叫這名字的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤和士  孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.01,0:04:50.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,似乎是個很可憐的人  所以要好好對待他哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:51.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟是個很可憐的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:55.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這  這樣麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也非常喜歡小姬的名字哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不僅覺得名字好  最重要的是很好念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:08.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,現在的孩子  名字不都很難念麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像閃亮亮名字什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:10.33,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：指那些偏離常識且很珍奇的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.87,0:05:15.08,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是唸錯了還會被家長狠狠地訓一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,學校的老師經常遇到的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:22.13,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還有  最近取動畫漫畫角色名字的也有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在這一點上  後藤老師漫畫裡的角色名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是絕不會有人取給小孩的  真令人安心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:27.51,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&HC3AC6B&\3c&H968465&\pos(1219.6,211.6)}緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.51,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&HC3AC6B&\3c&H968465&\pos(680.4,62.8)}緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.47,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\pos(1664.4,64.4)\c&HC3AC6B&\3c&H968465&}緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:28.51,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H3B63E7&\3c&H4338AF&\pos(1227.6,285.2)}襪帶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:31.47,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H3B63E7&\3c&H4338AF&\pos(717.2,66)}襪帶
