Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.68,0:05:34.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.93,0:05:36.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如你所言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,阿童木  不可以跑去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:45.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,給孩子取自己筆下角色的名字什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:46.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到底是種什麼心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我一輩子都感受不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,緊身褲  不可以跑去那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:55.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被取了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:58.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,乖  是個好孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:05:59.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,緊身褲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是個奇怪的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:06.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,下半身的樣子就像穿著緊身褲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:08.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真…可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬小姐  在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:14.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我在占卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:17.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,納德拉小姐的國家有占卜麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:19.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:20.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想測測嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:21.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:22.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,通過向精靈祈禱進行占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:31.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了  一直嗯嗯嗯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:35.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒  因為我是本名出道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:37.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,日子很難過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:42.29,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那樣的話  現在起用筆名不也挺好的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:43.84,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,200)\frz282.3\c&HD2BE8F&\3c&HB7AF5F&\pos(444.8,529.6)}掉落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.71,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(336,712)}鱗片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.71,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：「鱗片從眼睛裡掉出來」有「令人眼前一亮」「恍然大悟」的意思  源自聖經故事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.17,0:06:46.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一起想想？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.59,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(3.2,153.6)}暗騎士07@3rd
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:52.59,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自創作者龍騎士07
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:56.68,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\pos(1870,284)}周刊少年漫畫人總編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:56.68,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz270\pos(1450.4,390.8)}大和力郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:56.68,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：音同印刷排版切割
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:54.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這啥玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師的筆名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:59.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像下週開始就要用這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.81,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行麼  明明我也跟著一起思考過的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是出道前的新人還差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:14.49,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs55\pos(288.4,202)}副總編輯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:14.49,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\fs55\pos(261.2,576.8)}內木理佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.11,0:07:14.49,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：音同腰斬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.57,0:07:10.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作家名就是品牌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:14.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就跟商標一樣的  突然改變的話會使客人迷惑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:15.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.41,0:07:18.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我知道了  那我去告訴他不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:20.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他的態度很堅決麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:24.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他說「用現在的名字的話日子很難過」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:32.18,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an8}人聲嘈雜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:30.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:32.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是那個吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:36.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有沒有奇怪的占卜師在後藤老師那兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:40.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作家突然想要改名的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.18,0:07:44.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,背後其實是被這類人洗腦操縱的案例有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:47.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,工作室倒沒見過占卜師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:50.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有的話那應該就是在家裡了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個霧氣是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:54.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.83,0:07:57.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:03.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還真有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:05.88,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.38,0:08:07.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在占卜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.71,0:08:08.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.59,0:08:12.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,精靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.63,0:08:14.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,納德拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.05,0:08:16.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來了麼  精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是我喜歡的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咦  這位精靈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:30.53,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,78.4)}參考動畫第一話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,跟上次來我家的CEO很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,CEO？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你也來測測嗎  CEO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:37.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,CEO…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就是我真正的名字麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,志偉王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:46.17,kakushigoto in 6,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\c&H5A48CD&\frx10\fry342\frz20.03\org(806.4,222.4)\pos(398.4,166.4)}周刊少年漫畫人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.46,0:08:46.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟迷上奇怪的占卜師  靈能者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而變得奇怪的漫畫家有不少人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,像是突然開始改名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.30,kakushigoto in 10,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\frz12.16\pos(667.2,450.8)\c&H9DA3AF&}新名
