Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對話框裡的文本多到異常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.67,0:08:56.26,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1262.4,876.8)}※不是指柯南
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,用富氫水稀釋墨水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.47,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1451.2,857.6)\c&H498EA1&}墨汁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:01.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,發展到最後甚至有人堅信自己是神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:03.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,而成為了教主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:05.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.64,0:09:07.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:09.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有占卜師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:13.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是完全不是什麼可疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:18.07,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,完全全全  不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.53,0:09:19.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是…是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後呢  我也想改名了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,改成志偉王
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道說連你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:35.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}完全全全全全全全全…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,被洗腦的人都是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,{\an8}全全全全…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:46.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,聽我說  今天我和納德拉小姐一起看到精靈先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:47.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,精靈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.77,0:09:51.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為來的是個很沒有氣場的精靈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:53.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,納德拉小姐覺得很可惜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是麼  很可惜呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:01.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是  納德拉小姐說有件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即便不通過精靈先生來占卜也能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:08.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我和爸爸有個很強的守護靈跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,它一直保護著我們所以沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:20.26,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(908.8,454.4)\frz34.24\frx36\fry0}13歲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:21.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.43,0:10:26.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,雖然爸爸不怎麼信鬼靈這些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這個我就試著信信看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我還向精靈先生說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:37.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,「今後也請多多關照爸爸和我」了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:40.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:46.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我說  爸爸擅長畫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為…為什麼問起這事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,想起來我還從未看見過爸爸畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:56.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那畢竟是因為我在全力隱瞞著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.38,0:10:59.80,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,因為不擅長所以不畫麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也不能說不擅長…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:08.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這  我怎麼會在這種無聊的地方放不下自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:10.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那  是很擅長囉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.52,0:11:15.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,普普通通…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,作業  是風景的素描
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:21.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎  普通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實比普通還是稍微厲害一點…的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.46,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\frz333.7\pos(1041.6,662.4)}分鏡素描
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.46,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：標題源自蒼樹梅的漫畫「向陽素描」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.12,0:11:32.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,進退兩難了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:35.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,星期天我要和姬去寫生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.30,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,在想因畫得好被姬尊敬的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫得太好的話又會暴露我的職業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:42.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要畫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那多半是街道的風景之類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:50.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師您…不是好多年都沒畫過背景了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說什麼傻…傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:55.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,風景這種東西  我隨時都能畫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:57.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.86,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您不用擔心  不會暴露的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.53,0:12:04.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比新手好一點點的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:07.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,剛才的只是熱身
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:09.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,接下來我要認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:15.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,背景什麼的就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師您趕快去畫角色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這樣下去工作可就完不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:23.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,哇  這張畫得太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這怕是會暴露自己是職業漫畫家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那就有點傷腦筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:30.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,若是暴露自己是漫畫家的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.14,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有想過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.60,0:12:36.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,素描的風景畫要上色嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那肯定的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.98,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,又不是水墨畫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你問這個幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:42.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,突然想到自從我來了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:46.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,還一回都沒畫過彩頁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.20,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:55.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,說的也是  已經很多年都沒登過刊頭彩頁了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:12:58.67,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,求你不要往黑白色的原稿上色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.55,0:13:03.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這週我們又不是刊頭彩頁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\pos(840,148.8)\frz11.42\c&H9EE3F2&\3c&H517175&}藝術學校
