Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H435148&\frz11.49\pos(906,365.2)}繪畫教室
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H3F3F3F&\frz7.036\pos(947.6,629.2)\frx4\fry2}招募學生中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs40\c&H72ADD4&\3c&H617574&\frz14.32\pos(1293.2,758.8)}新手  小初高學生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs40\c&H72ADD4&\3c&H617574&\frz14.59\pos(1310.8,824.4)}也歡迎大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\fs35\c&H72ADD4&\3c&H617574&\frz13.65\pos(1341.2,893.2)}今日的教師是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.14,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\frz14.04\pos(1275.2,1028.8)}千田奈留{\bord3\fs35\c&H72ADD4&\3c&H617574&}老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.14,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H86CA2F&\3c&H1B1919&\pos(1144,771.2)}職業人士的尊嚴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.56,0:13:16.14,kakushigoto in 2,,0,0,0,,{\bord1\c&H8507DB&\3c&H3D4859&\pos(481.6,788.8)}姬的崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.65,0:13:24.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,早知道這樣就不該來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:26.40,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那麼  開始上課
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:34.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,小姬的爸爸  您怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:35.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你才是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我每週做一次志願者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,來這裡教小朋友們畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原  原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道您是來學習繪畫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:48.59,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個  這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:50.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:53.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,臉紅了  真是不知道他在害羞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.56,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,難道是假借來繪畫教室學習
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,實則是來見我的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這其中有很多原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:05.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這件事可要對姬保密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.90,0:14:06.82,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:08.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,話說回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:11.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你的繪畫技術已經好到能夠教別人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:14.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,其實…我已經獲得過好多次獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:16.54,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.96,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為了得到姬的崇拜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:21.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,暫且先捨棄我的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.50,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,向她請教吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:25.25,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:27.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我才是  拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.80,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H3E3B4A&\frz270\pos(188,242.8)}指請教學習
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:29.80,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H3E3B4A&\frz270\pos(1805.6,239.2)}指交往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:36.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫塑像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:38.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我倒是想畫能夠上色的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:40.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫得怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.94,0:14:42.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是我喜歡的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我指的是畫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真…真的嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:50.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是機會難得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:52.24,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我也想你提一些嚴格的建議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.99,0:14:55.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好是挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.99,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但硬要挑毛病的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比較像是漫畫風格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:03.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這張就比較像是北斗神拳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:07.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果讓畫漫畫的人畫素描
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,總是會犯職業病
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.26,0:15:11.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫得比較像是漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(1534.4,230.4)}聖喬治
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\an9}註：屠龍者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(74.8,185.6)}青年瑪爾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：羅馬十二主神之一，類似希臘的軍神阿瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto in 3,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(406.4,698.8)}阿里亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.21,0:15:11.97,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,{\pos(8,576)}註：希臘神話中幫助條賽給他毛線通過迷宮的公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是後藤老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:17.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,六條老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,您現在是要回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:22.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,繪畫教室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:24.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:27.90,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,後藤老師  難道您偷偷地在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:29.78,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,教別人畫畫是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:33.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,做志願者教別人畫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我太敬仰您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.32,0:15:38.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,確實  職業漫畫家的繪畫技術真是特別好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:42.33,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,如果你認為漫畫家也擅長畫一般的畫作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.33,0:15:43.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你就大錯特錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.34,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,漫畫好像被人稱作是綜合藝術
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:49.01,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,既要求能畫畫又要求能寫故事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:50.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.55,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.93,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我正是因為不能單憑繪畫和寫作生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.60,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才來畫漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:02.77,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但是您可不能插手姬的畫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.19,0:16:05.44,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這可是作業
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:08.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使您再疼愛她  作弊可是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.15,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我並沒有這個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.49,0:16:13.74,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.95,0:16:15.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我可是會認真檢查的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.57,0:16:16.28,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:18.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,就因為我是職業漫畫家這一原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.37,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然讓姬陷入到了明明是自己獨立完成的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,卻要受到不正當評價的處境
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.71,0:16:27.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,看來只能讓她親眼看到姬獨自畫畫的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.42,0:16:28.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,才能證明姬的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.05,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你星期天有空嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.97,0:16:35.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我希望你能和我一起去動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:38.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,一  一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這…這難道是約會的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:45.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:47.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:50.19,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,然後  到了星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,和姬一起出門  真是興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.58,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:04.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,有好多動物呢  確實挺讓人困擾的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:17.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我該怎麼做呢  畫什麼才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.34,0:17:19.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬你就畫自己喜歡的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:23.14,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\pos(1112,329.6)\c&H626069&}老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.81,0:17:24.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我決定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.06,0:17:25.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我要畫老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.73,0:17:35.03,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺這個約會好奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.53,0:17:37.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,居然叫我不要被人發現默默看著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.86,0:17:41.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畢竟要是讓人看見老師和學生家長一起約會
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.12,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,可就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.29,0:17:45.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你可要看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:47.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這可是姬自己一個人畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:51.42,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.51,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,啊  是老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你們在這裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們是來完成老師布置的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:04.02,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師你是因為星期天一個人太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:05.27,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以才來動物園是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人家才不寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:09.06,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,人家可是在約會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來就和「剩女單身婚禮」那種東西一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,約會的對像我可是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.11,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.95,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,他…與我咫尺天涯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,咫尺天涯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.79,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.92,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我們竟然這麼不懂事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.38,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.67,0:18:36.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師的戀人居然已經不在這個世上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:40.26,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師肯定是因為受到了打擊才瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:43.18,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以才自己一個人約會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:47.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要好好觀察後再畫哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:50.23,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸你不畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.23,0:18:52.94,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,畫…畫喲  當然畫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.86,0:18:55.52,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我對畫風景沒什麼自信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:57.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以才叫姬來的動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,好像我更不擅長畫動物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,它藏在洞裡了  看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:06.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.62,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,只能憑想像畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:13.46,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,憑想像畫的話就很像漫畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.71,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,從洞裡可以看見它的眼睛在放光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:21.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老虎能看見我們這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:24.72,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,應該能看見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:29.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,到最後它都還是沒能從洞裡出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:33.31,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這一切你都見證了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:35.61,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,真是一次美妙的約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:40.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,約會真的讓人好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:44.16,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老師好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:47.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,明天我會乖乖的  老師你可要振作起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.66,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒能畫成  真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我畫好了喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:56.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,憑想像畫好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.04,0:19:58.17,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是看著畫的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.00,0:20:00.84,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不是看不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:02.47,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,所以我畫的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:07.10,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,老虎眼中的我和爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.60,0:20:09.35,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.89,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,果然是憑想像的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:16.73,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不對哦  我可是看著老虎畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.36,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,你這都第幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:24.70,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:28.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要怎麼處理在動物園打高爾夫這個場景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:31.41,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,能畫動物的人已經沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.87,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,我有一個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:39.25,kakushigoto in 2 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\fs55\frz270\c&H6D6E71&\move(1802.4,200.8,1728,232,0,3864)}好多獅子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.09,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使不用畫極其費事的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.21,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,也能夠表現出動物園的場景
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:44.43,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,從動物的視角
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,不愧是老手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,隨機應變的能力果然與眾不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:49.43,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\c&H3D3C4D&\pos(659.2,798.4)}在遇到困難時經常使用的一種手法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:50.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,比如
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:52.31,kakushigoto in 4,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\pos(356.8,246.4)\c&H616161&}火災
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.27,0:20:52.22,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.44,kakushigoto in 10 - zong,,0,0,0,,{\frz270\c&H616161&\pos(1902.4,382.4)}怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.39,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,怪獸來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:56.69,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,即使不直接畫出來也能夠表現出來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.48,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,這就是職業人士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:01.32,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,感覺就像是低成本電影一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:07.57,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,裝飾起來好羞恥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.49,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,為什麼呢  畫得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,爸爸可是下了血本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.91,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,買來了最貴的畫框
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:17.75,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,根本就和房子不協調
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:18.83,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:22.63,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,但感覺好像在哪裡見到過這幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.60,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\pos(1112,329.6)\c&H626069&}老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:34.85,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.60,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\c&H5280DC&\frz1.905\pos(556.8,435.2)}照相紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:38.60,kakushigoto in 7,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\fs50\frz2.3\pos(571.2,614.4)\c&H5EB4E7&}一張1000日元
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.77,kakushigoto in,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,0)\pos(820.8,971.2)\c&H4E4EA2&}動物RASIA
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.77,kakushigoto tip,,0,0,0,,註：源自橫濱動物園愛稱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:46.45,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,沒錯  以前我們仨也一起去那拍了這樣一張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.29,0:21:55.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,那幅畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.33,0:21:58.04,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,是從她的視角畫的吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,——————ED——————
