Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:36.08,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}將離別的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:45.84,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}ポケットに匿していたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:45.84,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}隱藏在口袋中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:52.93,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}想い出は  モノクローム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.13,0:22:52.93,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}回憶是單色相片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:58.48,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}色を点けてくれ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:58.48,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}給我點上顏色吧
