Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.98,0:23:06.73,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}再一次來到我的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.78,kakushigoto ed jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}はなやいで  うるわしの Color Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.90,0:23:11.78,kakushigoto ed ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fade(300,300)}花枝招展的  美麗的Color Girl
