Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:34.76,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,要是我被關起來熬夜趕稿  姬可是會寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:35.97,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,房間我已經準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:36.68,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,關起來？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:40.64,kakushigoto text,,0,0,0,,姬——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:41.02,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\i1\c&H000000&\pos(728,356.8)}即使如此依然輪番上陣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.72,0:23:41.02,kakushigoto in 3 - heng,,0,0,0,,{\fs65\i1\c&H000000&\pos(843.2,664)}住下來了！
